outputs.output_descr: The project “Building a better future for citizens of Fushë Kosovë/Kosovo Polje and Obiliq/Obilić” is a joint effort of UNDP, UNICEF,UNFPA, UNV and WHO under UN Kosovo Team (UNKT) umbrella, addressing key human security challenges

project_descr: Building a better future for citizens of FushëKosovë/Kosovo Polje and Obiliq/Obilic: Participation, Protection, and multi-ethnic Partnerships for improved education, health and sustainable livelihoods
project_title: Building better future for citizens of 2 Municipalities
